{
    "esm": "0.4.0",
    "metadata": {
        "name": "MeanFreePath",
        "description": "Mean free path of air molecules. Migrated from Aerosol.jl@c8c640bb src/single_particle_dynamics.jl:22 (`MeanFreePath` @component). Calculates the mean free path from dynamic viscosity, pressure, molecular weight, and temperature (Seinfeld & Pandis 2006, Chapter 9, Eq. 9.6).",
        "tags": [
            "aerosol",
            "particle-dynamics",
            "mean-free-path"
        ],
        "created": "2026-05-07T00:00:00Z",
        "authors": [
            "Aerosol.jl contributors",
            "EarthSciModels migration (esm-nsj)"
        ],
        "references": [
            {
                "citation": "Seinfeld, J. H. and Pandis, S. N. (2006) Atmospheric Chemistry and Physics, 2nd Edition, Chapter 9, Eq. 9.6."
            }
        ]
    },
    "models": {
        "MeanFreePath": {
            "reference": {
                "notes": "source_ref: Aerosol.jl@c8c640bb636b22f2425460e9ed5cba50793bfee1:src/single_particle_dynamics.jl:22\nUpstream `MeanFreePath` is an MTK `@component` with three constants (R, M_air, π_val), three parameters (T, P, μ), and one variable (λ). The equation is:\n  • λ ~ 2 * μ / (P * sqrt(8 * M_air / (π_val * R * T)))  (Eq. 9.6 — mean free path)\nThe equation is algebraic (no derivatives), making this an observed-only component.\n\nObservability classification: observed-only — the single output λ is given by an algebraic equation. Test scenarios use `time_span: [0, 1]` and sample at t=0.\n\nTolerance rationale (model-level rel=1e-9): observed-only algebraic system (no ODE integration); the equation involves multiplication, division, and sqrt. Floating-point round-off is ~1e-15. 1e-9 leaves comfortable headroom."
            },
            "tolerance": {
                "rel": 1.0e-9
            },
            "variables": {
                "R": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "J/(mol*K)",
                    "default": 8.314,
                    "description": "Molar gas constant"
                },
                "M_air": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "kg/mol",
                    "default": 0.02897,
                    "description": "Molecular weight of air"
                },
                "π_val": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "1",
                    "default": 3.141592653589793,
                    "description": "Pi (dimensionless)"
                },
                "T": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "K",
                    "default": 298.15,
                    "description": "Temperature"
                },
                "P": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "Pa",
                    "default": 101325.0,
                    "description": "Pressure"
                },
                "μ": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "kg/(m*s)",
                    "default": 1.8e-5,
                    "description": "Dynamic viscosity of air"
                },
                "λ": {
                    "type": "state",
                    "units": "m",
                    "description": "Mean free path of air"
                }
            },
            "equations": [
                {
                    "lhs": "λ",
                    "rhs": {
                        "op": "/",
                        "args": [
                            { "op": "*", "args": [2, "μ"] },
                            {
                                "op": "*",
                                "args": [
                                    "P",
                                    {
                                        "op": "sqrt",
                                        "args": [
                                            {
                                                "op": "/",
                                                "args": [
                                                    { "op": "*", "args": [8, "M_air"] },
                                                    {
                                                        "op": "*",
                                                        "args": [
                                                            "π_val",
                                                            {
                                                                "op": "*",
                                                                "args": ["R", "T"]
                                                            }
                                                        ]
                                                    }
                                                ]
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    }
                                ]
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                }
            ],
            "tests": [
                {
                    "id": "default_conditions",
                    "description": "Default conditions: T = 298.15 K, P = 101325 Pa, μ = 1.8e-5 kg/(m*s). λ = 2*1.8e-5 / (101325 * sqrt(8*0.02897 / (π*8.314*298.15))) ≈ 6.513e-8 m.",
                    "time_span": { "start": 0.0, "end": 1.0 },
                    "assertions": [
                        { "variable": "λ", "time": 0.0, "expected": 6.512744e-08, "tolerance": { "rel": 1.0e-4 } }
                    ]
                }
            ],
            "examples": [
                {
                    "id": "temperature_dependence",
                    "description": "Sweep temperature from 250 K to 350 K to show how mean free path varies with temperature (λ ∝ sqrt(T)).",
                    "initial_state": {
                        "type": "per_variable",
                        "values": {}
                    },
                    "parameters": {
                        "P": 101325.0,
                        "μ": 1.8e-5
                    },
                    "time_span": { "start": 0.0, "end": 1.0 },
                    "parameter_sweep": {
                        "type": "cartesian",
                        "dimensions": [
                            {
                                "parameter": "T",
                                "range": { "start": 250.0, "stop": 350.0, "count": 50 }
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    "plots": [
                        {
                            "id": "mfp_vs_temperature",
                            "type": "line",
                            "description": "Mean free path vs temperature — shows λ ∝ sqrt(T) through the sqrt dependence in Eq. 9.6.",
                            "x": { "variable": "T", "label": "T (K)" },
                            "y": { "variable": "λ", "label": "λ (m)" }
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        }
    }
}
